184
00:11:40,029 --> 00:11:42,029
Anda mengetahui keberadaan Lee Kyung Ja.

185
00:11:49,810 --> 00:11:51,009
Kang Chi Soo.

186
00:11:51,279 --> 00:11:54,009
Anda ingin menjadikannya pembunuh, tapi akhirnya gagal.

187
00:11:54,210 --> 00:11:56,479
Lalu Anda diam-diam mencoba membunuh Jaksa Do

188
00:11:56,479 --> 00:11:58,820
